<plot>Sponsored by the makers of the Encyclopedia Americana, this quiz show featured questions on obscure bits of American folklore and history that had been sent in by home viewers. Originally, the contestants on the program were adults, but the show later switched to having high school students compete.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?035309</url></doc>
